<!-- Intent -->
<div id="intent-help" class="help-text">
	<h4>Intent</h4>
	<p>On this screen the user is asked to define the intent of the philanthropic and fundraising activity. The intent is broken down into three elements (1) socio-economic priority, (2) impact and timeframe and artistic/cultural positioning.</p> 
	<p>Socio-economic priority: E.g. "We want to raise aspirations and increase employment."</p>
	<p>Impact and timeframe: E.g. "Reducing inequality to UK average levels and doubling the size of the creative sector by the end of the decade".</p>
	<p>Artistic/Cultural Positioning: E.g. "By turning our joint and diverse heritage into an innovation engine for the local economy".</p>
</div>
