<!-- Themes -->
<div id="themes-help" class="help-text">
	<h4>Themes</h4>
	<p>On this screen the user is asked to identify the priority themes for Philanthropy and Fundraising.  The themes can be one of three types: (1) Target Market, (2) Core Service and (3) Infrastructure Support.  These options are shown by the dropdown arrow to the right of the box.</p>
	<p>E.g. (For the 'Raise Aspirations' intent) </p>
	<p>Target Market: "Working class boys 8-13 years of ethnicity groups"</p>
	<p>Core Services: "Schools outreach sessions (joint and shared heritage), school visits."</p>
	<p>Infrastructure support: "Joint and shared heritage materials development, project management, onsite classrooms."</p>
	<p>You can add additional themes by clicking 'Add New Priority Theme'.</p>
</div>
